  "content": "<h1>Combat</h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2 class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">Chat: Attack roll</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family: Signika, sans-serif;\">Figure 2: Attack roll modifer</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\"><img style=\"font-family: Signika, sans-serif;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/dmGj5Q8/Screenshot-2021-02-18-at-14-19-37.webp\" alt=\"Attack roll in chat\" width=\"391\" height=\"97\" /></span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 7px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">When you click to make an Attack roll it shows a dialog where you can add Banes and Boons to your roll. Your GM will tell you if and how many to add. Boons are a positive number and Banes a negative. Each Boon/Bane will add an extra d6 to your roll.&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">Boon: The dice with the highest number will be added to your roll.&nbsp;</span><br /><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">Bane: The dice with the highest number will be subtracted&nbsp;from your roll.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family: Signika, sans-serif;\">Figure 3: Attack roll in chat</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/QmdftH5/Screenshot-2021-02-18-at-14-30-08.webp\" alt=\"Attack roll in chat\" width=\"300\" height=\"194\" /></span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">The chat shows:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul1\" style=\"font-size: medium;\">\n<li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">The characters name</li>\n<li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">Ancestry</li>\n<li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">The characters highest Path</li>\n<li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">An image of the weapon used</li>\n<li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">Name of the weapon</li>\n<li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">Name of a taget if selected</li>\n<li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">The attribute use in the attack</li>\n<li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">The defense of a choosen target if a target is slected.</li>\n<li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">A button to roll damage.</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Signika, sans-serif;\">Figure 4: Attack troll in chat with talents active</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/bbxHtpW/Screenshot-2021-02-18-at-14-45-32.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"304\" height=\"368\" /></p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 36px; text-indent: -36px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">An advanced example:</p>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"p1\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">Hover on Attack roll shows the dice rolled. d20 + Strength modifer + 1 Boon (if multiple the highest is selected).</span></li>\n<li class=\"p1\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">A list of all effects (talents) active for this attack. 1 Boon to attack. Extra damage +1d6 and an extra 1d6 if roll is above 20+.</span></li>\n<li class=\"p1\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">Two buttons for damage rolls.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">Support for using the Foundry Target system and if one don't want to use it.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica;\">Chat: Creature rolls</span></h3>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">By default only the GM sees the attack result and Defense (target number) value of the creature. The roll is not shown and the players can't hover over the result and see the modifiers of the creature.</p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">This can be changed in the System setttings.</p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family: Signika, sans-serif;\">Figure 5: System settings</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/LtPBRnS/Screenshot-2021-02-19-at-10-05-46.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"561\" height=\"91\" /></p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">&nbsp;</p>",
